 2. the pakistani is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
 3. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the canadian##1
 4. the german is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person who's birthday is in february##2
 5. the fan of disco is the person drinking fanta##1
 6. the fan of folk is on the far right##1
 7. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in february is between the person who's sport is rugby and the person who's hobby is writing##2
 9. the person who's sport is baseball is the person who's hobby is writing##1
10. the person who's hobby is chess is on the far left##1
11. the fan of disco is the person who's sport is golf##1
12. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
13. the malaysian is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
14. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the german##1

